Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:06.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Alright, ponies, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:08.61,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We're all ears, right, Bulk Biceps?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:13.24,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Yeh, nu-uh, I'm all… muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:14.81,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I like your attitude, Bulk Biceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:22.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But it's gonna take more than muscles and yeahs to get us to the Equestria Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:25.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We are the aerial relay team,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and it's up to the three of us to make sure that we qualify at the trials!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:32.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And do I need to remind you, how much I…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:36.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I mean, Ponyville wants to qualify and make it to the Games?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:42.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I remember. I really, really, really wanna qualify for you and Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:43.35,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:46.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Give me a "P" for Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:49.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"P" - Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.03,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,P!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:53.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:57.25,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That was a scary… I mean, great cheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:01:01.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just make sure that you'll have one ready for when we qualify for the aerial relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:05.35,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,And after that, for when we'll get gold at the Equestrian Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:07.07,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:11.86,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna be good, you're gonna be better with some of my apple brown bettys in ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,They're perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.18,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"P" is for "perfect"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:19.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Alright, team,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:22.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,show me what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Put some bend into those knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Flap those wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:29.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And I wanna see all four hooves off the ground on the count of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:32.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,One-two-three!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:43.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to breathe while you're up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.66,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"P" is for…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.16,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"pain"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sorry we couldn't fly with you on the aerial relay,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:49.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but the air sprinters needed us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Too bad we can only compete in one event,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but rules are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:56.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It was nice of you to be part of the team that doesn't have…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the strongest flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nothing nice about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:08.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know that I can pick up the slack for anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:11.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,With me on the team, we'll qualify. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ponyville is very lucky to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:22.89,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I am so proud to be representing Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:28.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's such an honor to even try out for the Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:31.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I just hope I don't let anypony down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:32.63,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,We'll make them proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.31,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"P" is for "proud"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.14,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be the best fans anypony has ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Cannot wait to see what everypony else is wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:46.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Even though I am absolutely sure they won't be better than the Ponyville uniforms I'm designing for the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:51.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And we will make it to the Games once everypony carbo-loads on my apple brown betties!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.66,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.47,Somepony,,0,0,0,,There's Rainbow Dash! She's an awesome flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I heard that she's flying at the last third of the relay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:39.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,which means everypony else is gonna have to be way ahead to beat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:44.81,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:47.39,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I hear they're flying for Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Then Cloudsdale will definitely qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.39,Somepony,,0,0,0,,They're the best flyers ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.15,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,And the game is on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.99,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Huh, nice to see there's some real competition here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:02.39,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Two more days of practice, then we'll see you in the air, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.61,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,If you're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ah, the Wonderbolts know a winner when they see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And we'll be winners just as soon as we practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Right, team?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.64,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:16.69,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:22.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Give us some clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.14,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Give us some dale!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And what do you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.82,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Where can I get pom-poms like those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:40.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, do I need to remind you of what our goal is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.39,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Uh, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We want to qualify!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:47.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We need to be one of  the first four teams to cross the finish line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:51.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Bulk Biceps, you're the first flyer, so let me see you flap it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What the?..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Got the idea from them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Push down! Cakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.34,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Looks like they got better aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:16.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, the passing of the baton needs to be seamless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:20.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't miss a wingbeat, or drop a hair in altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And whatever you do, don't let go of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Are you really, really, really sure you're ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:29.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't want to take it if you're not super-sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:31.32,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Ponyville can do so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'll be back with a freshly painted one in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We were using that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:48.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And it's not like anypony else has color-coordinated horseshoes or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess, some ponies do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Some ponies do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:07:00.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Have a better chance of qualifying and going to the Equestria Games than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Watch and learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:14.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The Cloudsdales are Wonderbolts, and Wonderbolts are the best flyers there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And my personal heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, maybe you can learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Please, learn something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.92,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Come on, Soarin, pick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.53,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,You can do better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.95,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:35.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Prac-tice! Prac-tice! Yaaay, practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.35,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.70,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:58.41,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:00.50,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,As good as any Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.61,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rainbow Dash, I'm just so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:07.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You scooped Soarin out of the sky and brought him down to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.03,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And now, now he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,At least, I hope he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.51,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Oh, my wing hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:19.45,Soarin,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure it'll be okay by the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.15,Soarin,,0,0,0,,You're the best, Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ah, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.91,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But if you're feel like talking about how great I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:35.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,don't let me stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.19,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,"P" for Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.53,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Um, "Rainbow Dash" actually starts with an "R".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.83,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Nevermind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tough break to lose a teammate for the tryouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.73,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:51.73,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,You grew up in Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.34,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,So that means you could fly with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:55.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.06,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,We mean, practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.63,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,You could practice with us until Soarin's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.95,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.93,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Wanna be our third?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,My team really needs me to be at my best in order to qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna be too worn out when the race comes around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:19.58,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,We put you through some pretty intense workouts at the Wonderbolt Academy and you handled those just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:23.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Heh, I did kick some major tail at the Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:28.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But I don't know how my teammates will feel about me practicing with the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.09,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Who said they need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:35.61,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Think about it, Rainbow Dash! This is your chance to fly with the winners!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.26,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Wise decision, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.32,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ready, ponies, ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Fly on, fly on, fly on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, Bulk Biceps. You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to take the horseshoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.61,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,If you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You, keep doing your wing-ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.81,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna go get some… water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:42.47,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's not easy practicing with two teams, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Does anypony else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:07.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No. they're too busy practicing to wonder why you keep disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:11.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, I've seen the other teams practicing and we're still gonna qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can fly fast enough to make up the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:19.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It just seems like one of the teams you're practicing with needs a little more help than the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:23.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But it's so much more fun working out with the winners than, um, the…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,non-winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Besides, Ponyville will still qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:29.13,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.10,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You've got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:35.90,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,You can really be an asset to our team. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:40.23,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,We want you to join the Cloudsdale team. Permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.30,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,It loooks like Soarin's wing won't heal in time for the trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.30,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,We want you to fly with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:51.44,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Of course, this means you won't be able to fly for Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.13,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,But let's face it. Even if you're on their team,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.02,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,their chances of qualifying to the game are pretty slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.75,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,So, what's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Take some time to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:12.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,They want me to fly with them! It's like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:17.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If you fly for Cloudsdale, Pinkie Pie will not have anypony to cheer for,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:20.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity's uniforms will never be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and Applejack will have slaved over those apple brownberries for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But I really want to fly with the best team!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think this is a decision you have to make on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The race is tomorrow, so you better make it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Woe is me! Woe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:01.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've hurt my hoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:03.96,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:08.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,tripped on a hoof
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and landed on a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,pockey stick
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:18.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,If I get my hoofs on it, , it'll be in a big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:23.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can fly now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:25.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll be better by try-outs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:31.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll be lucky if I ever fly again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll just need a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:40.46,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry, Rainbow Dash. We'll take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:45.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,At least somepony will, like a medic or a doctor or a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:54.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, the medic pony isn't sure what's wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Everything, absolutely everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:00.07,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This'll cure everything that ails you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:05.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I couldn't have done that on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:09.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Nothing says "get better" like a little medical pizazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Silk slings and a glitter bandage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And how is our patient doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:27.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to let you know that we're so sorry you're hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:30.61,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but you shouldn't worry a bit about not being able to be in the tryouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We'll be alright. We even have a replacement!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We're so, so sorry that you can't compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.37,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We all know how much you love to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.81,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And we promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.48,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Cross our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:50.08,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That if we qualify and make it to the Equestria Games and all win gold medals,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.84,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,you can have ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:55.44,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Because we know how much a gold medal means to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:02.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,, I think Rainbow Dash might need to rest some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your beanies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know, choosing not to choose isn't really a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:16.80,Soarin,,0,0,0,,You sure have nice friends. Nopony has been by to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.02,Soarin,,0,0,0,,They're too busy practicing, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, hopefully your wing will be better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:27.08,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine. I'm just keeping it warm in case my team wants me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:29.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, wants you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Spitfire and Fleetfoot told me you were still too injured to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:37.15,Soarin,,0,0,0,,And they told me that they worried I won't be one hundred percent by the tryouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.69,Soarin,,0,0,0,,So they were going with somepony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That somepony else was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:45.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Until, well, untill I got hurt, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:49.13,Soarin,,0,0,0,,So, I guess we're all outta luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:52.40,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale won't qualify without three flyers, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:55.13,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Ponyville won't qualify without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.67,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:16.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Even with Rainbow Dash's replacement I don't think we're gonna qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No offence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:22.16,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do with all these now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:25.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What were you gonna do with them before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:30.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Maybe my Equestria Games uniforms will still be in style next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:32.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I mean, I am pretty fashion-forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:40.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is that Rainbow Dash walking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.01,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you're feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I feel great because…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I was never hurt in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:00.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I faked my injury so I wouldn't have to choose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,between flying for Ponyville or Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:07.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I wanted to fly with you both, and the decision was too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.96,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rainbow Dash, you don't have to choose us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:15.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know you love to win, and you should go with the team that surely will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know now who I should have been loyal to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:21.06,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Good choice. Always stick with the winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:27.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Because it's not just where I live, but it's where my friends are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.81,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The ponies who really care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whether I can help them win a race or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.24,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's the right decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:43.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You lied to me about Soarin's wing just so you could get a better flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:49.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You may be a winning team, but you're still not the kind of team I want to be a part of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:54.03,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, you are something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:58.11,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Saw that at the academy, seeing it again here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.91,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,We can learn a lot from a competitor like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.00,Fleetfoot,,0,0,0,,Think we already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.17,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Ready to fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.29,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.12,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Never should've lied and tried to replace you to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:14.19,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Go, Cloudsdale!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ponyville relay team!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We've got a race to get ready for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.37,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.62,Soarin,,0,0,0,,Come on Ponyville! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Go, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:01.57,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Qualify, Ponyville! Qualify, Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:04.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Go, Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:20.41,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ponyville qualifies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:57.91,BulkBiceps,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:06.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Equestria Games, here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:12.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I can't deny it. I love to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:16.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I ever have to choose between winning and being loyal to my friends, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:19.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm always gonna choose my friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:26.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cause as much as I love winning, I love them wa-a-ay more.{\i0}
